       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CARDADV.
      *> Demo: the called program name is hidden inside a copybook and only
      *> revealed by COPY ... REPLACING. The default parser does not expand
      *> copybooks, so it never sees the CALL; the advanced backend's COPY/REPLACING
      *> expander (preprocess) inlines it and the CALL to REALSUB becomes visible.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-PARM        PIC X(10).
       01  WS-STATUS      PIC S9(4).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN.
           MOVE 'CARD' TO WS-PARM.
           COPY CALLBOOK REPLACING ==:SUBPGM:== BY ==REALSUB==.
           GOBACK.
